Module JavaDataStructures

Package JavaDS.Trees

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    INode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Interface for all one dimensional tree node based objects to implement containing shared functionality for any type of tree the underlying node might belong to.
    ITree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Interface for all one dimensional tree based data structures.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Main super class for nodes contained within binary based tree data structures.
    BinarySearchTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Class implementing the Binary Search Tree data structure and related algorithms.
    BinaryTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Main super class implement common functionality shared across all different types of binary trees.
    NAryNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Main super class for nodes contained with N-ary derived tress.
    SuperNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Main node super class containing shared logic for nodes that might be contained in any type of underlying, one dimensional tree structures the node might be populated within.
    SuperTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    Main tree structure class containing shared logic for any underlying, one dimensional tree based data structure to extend from.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TraversalDirection
    Enum to represent directional options for tree traversal.
